50|$|The {{parties to}} the {{arbitration}} commit themselves to voluntarily comply with the judgement of the Arbitration Court. The parties and the Arbitration Court take all possible efforts for the Arbitration Court's judgement <b>to</b> <b>be</b> legally <b>enforceable.</b> In the event of failure {{to comply with the}} judgement of the Arbitration Court voluntarily, the enforcement procedures envisaged by the legislation of Russia are used, and as concerns the judgements on foreign trade disputes - those envisaged by international conventions.|$|R
